      "message": "Dash are to trim whitespace, before \"{{- \" or after \" -}}\"\nThe issue here is that assumption is made that .Values.aaf.enabled could be inherited from the onap/values.yaml file, but that's not the case, hence helm is not able to evaluate the variable: <.Values.aaf.enabled>: can't evaluate field",
